title: Avengers TPB (v1 - v5) (2013 - 2014) (Digital-HC) (Broadcast+Zon
description:
Avengers TPB (v1 - v5) (2013 - 2014) (Digital-HC) (Broadcast+Zone-Empire)


As part of Marvel NOW!, the team heads off in a new direction, expanding their roster and their sphere of influence to a global and even interplanetary level. The series is continued from Avengers Vol.4.

Collected Editions

Vol. 1: Avengers World (#1-6)
Vol. 2: The Last White Event (#7-11)
Vol. 3: Prelude to Infinity (#12-17)
Vol. 4: Infinity (#18-23)
Vol. 5: Adapt Or Die (#24-28)
